{
  "texts": [
    "An overwhelming majority of 96 percent said they do not have those guidelines; only four percent possess such guidelines.",
    "Third, we asked if their institutions, at least, opened discussions that would lead to policy formation regarding the practical and ethical use of these tools.",
    "A minority of 28 percent claimed they had initiated such discussions, but a clear majority of 72 percent indicated they had not started such talks.",
    "Fourth, we asked if the educators, in their capacity, have provided guidelines for their students in the subjects they taught.",
    "Only 11 percent of the respondents provided guidelines, while the majority of 89 percent did not."
  ]
}